      "name": "Bench-top hemolysis RH index comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index compared against in-vitro modified index of hemolysis measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. RH < 1 at all operating points; mean absolute error 0.07 RH units across the test matrix."
