    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 for Model Risk Level 2. CFD-predicted RH index satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at all 5 operating points with a maximum deviation of 11.3% from bench measurements. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for a Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
